errEither.data.foo.either: conflicting values true and int (mismatched types bool and int):
    ./datatest/tests.cue:27:21
    1:242
    1:533
errEither.data.foo.either: conflicting values true and string (mismatched types bool and string):
    ./datatest/tests.cue:27:21
    1:533
errEither.data.foo.either: invalid value true (does not satisfy matchN): 0 matched, expected >=1:
    1:232
    ./datatest/tests.cue:27:21
-- out/generate-v3/errKind --
errKind.data.foo.kind: conflicting values "widget" and "other":
    ./datatest/tests.cue:15:19
